==拍攝==
《搞事樂園》是在2007年12月至2008年1月在[[匹茲堡|匹茲堡]], [[賓夕凡尼亞州|賓夕凡尼亞州]]拍攝。大部份場景都是在Kennywood遊樂場內拍攝。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/842/842923p1.html |title=Adventureland News |author=Kaleem Aftab |date=2007-12-21 |publisher=IGN Entertainment |accessdate=2008-10-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080928201538/http://movies.ign.com/articles/842/842923p1.html |archivedate=2008年9月28日 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

==發行==
電影在2009年的[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]舉行首映。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://festival.sundance.org/2009/film_events/films/adventureland |title = Adventureland 2009 Sundance Film Festival Premiere |accessdate = 2009-11-17 |publisher = [[List_of_films_at_the_2009_Sundance_Film_Festival|List of films at the 2009 Sundance Film Festival]] |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090311005128/http://festival.sundance.org/2009/film_events/films/adventureland |archivedate = 2009年3月11日 }}</ref> 之後在2009年4月3日全國上映。電影也在2009年的[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]國際電影節上映。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/journalists/tim-robey/5652767/Edingburgh-Film-Festival-The-Hurt-Locker-Adventureland-Moon.html |title=Edinburgh Film Festival: The Hurt Locker, Adventureland, Moon |last=Robey |first=Tim |date=2009-06-26 |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |accessdate=2013-03-23 |archive-date=2018-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817193418/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/journalists/tim-robey/5652767/Edingburgh-Film-Festival-The-Hurt-Locker-Adventureland-Moon.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

